@node MAIN "Welcome"

    Remote Access ©2001 @{"Dietmar Eilert" link COPYRIGHT}

    @{b}ABSTRACT@{ub}

    RA is a shared library project which simplifies the task of running other
    applications  to show documents (a typical use of RA is a "Link to my web
    site" button in applications).

